{"id":13760,"date":"2022-08-15T16:24:15","date_gmt":"2022-08-15T09:24:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=13760"},"modified":"2022-08-20T16:27:07","modified_gmt":"2022-08-20T09:27:07","slug":"6-sai-lam-khi-cham-soc-oto-vao-mua-dong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/6-sai-lam-khi-cham-soc-oto-vao-mua-dong\/","title":{"rendered":"6 sai l\u1ea7m khi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u00f4t\u00f4 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"article__sapo cms-desc\">M\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, \u00f4t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1edfi th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t, nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5p l\u00e0m xe hay g\u1eb7p s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 h\u01a1n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 6 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i khi &#8220;ch\u0103m&#8221; xe trong th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft gi\u00e1 l\u1ea1nh.<\/div>\n<div class=\"article__body cms-body \">\n<p><strong>1. Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u00e1y li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u1ea5m xe<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u1ea5m xe trong m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Ch\u01b0a t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 h\u1ea1i cho \u1eafc-quy xe.<\/p>\n<p>Theo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u00f4t\u00f4 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n mi\u1ec7ng th\u00ec b\u1ea1n n\u00ean k\u00e9o b\u01b0\u1edbm gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1. Ngo\u00e0i ra s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1eafc-quy d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00edch n\u1ed5 l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p><strong>2. Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea1y xe kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00f3ng m\u00e1y<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean, nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ee7 xe c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng xe tr\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea1y xe kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea3i trong th\u1eddi gian kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00f3ng m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 v\u00e0 bugi b\u1ecb l\u00e3o h\u00f3a, gi\u1ea3m tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd c\u1ee7a xe r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<\/p>\n<div class=\"article-photo inlinephoto\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/qjwwpdhnw\/2017_11_09\/chamsoc1_CQHQ.jpg.ashx?width=600\" data-desc=\"Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u00f4t\u00f4 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o\" data-index=\"0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/qjwwpdhnw\/2017_11_09\/chamsoc1_CQHQ.jpg.ashx?width=600\" alt=\"6 sai l\u1ea7m khi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u00f4t\u00f4 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh 1\" width=\"600\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/qjwwpdhnw\/2017_11_09\/chamsoc1_CQHQ.jpg.ashx?width=600\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<div>H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c xe v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u00f4ng minh, m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t c\u0169ng t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng xe ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t b\u00f4i tr\u01a1n n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m n\u00f3ng xe tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<\/div>\n<p><strong>3. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u0103m s\u00f3c l\u1ed1p v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong m\u00f9a n\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 cao m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ed1p \u00f4t\u00f4, ngay c\u1ea3 trong m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed kh\u00f4 xe l\u00e0m h\u1ea1i l\u1edbp cao su \u1edf ph\u1ea7n l\u1ed1p xe.<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed1p xe non h\u01a1i s\u1ebd t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00e1m \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a xe, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd c\u1ee7a l\u1ed1p xe v\u00e0 ti\u00eau t\u1ed1n nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u h\u01a1n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng c\u0169ng v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n l\u1ed1p xe th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean do kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed b\u1ecb \u1ea9m \u1edf b\u00ean trong l\u1ed1p s\u1ebd d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i.<\/p>\n<p><strong>4. L\u01a1 l\u00e0 v\u1ec7 sinh n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00a0<\/strong>M\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, d\u00f9 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft m\u01b0a ph\u00f9n hay hanh kh\u00f4 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ee5i b\u00e1m v\u00e0 vi khu\u1ea9n k\u00fd sinh tr\u00ean n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t xe ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n nhanh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u da, n\u1ec9\u2026<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1c khe vi\u1ec1n \u1edf c\u1eeda c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i b\u00e1m b\u1ee5i. Nh\u1eefng b\u1ee5i b\u1eb7m n\u00e0y g\u00e2y ra m\u00f9i \u1ea9m m\u1ed1c, m\u1ea5t t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, v\u1eeba g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho xe v\u1eeba g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00e0ng n\u00ean v\u1ec7 sinh xe th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec3 xe kh\u00f4 r\u00e1o, th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng.<\/p>\n<div class=\"article-photo inlinephoto\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/qjwwpdhnw\/2017_11_09\/chamsoc2_SGQM.jpg\" data-desc=\"Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u00f4t\u00f4 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o\" data-index=\"1\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/qjwwpdhnw\/2017_11_09\/chamsoc2_SGQM.jpg\" alt=\"6 sai l\u1ea7m khi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u00f4t\u00f4 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh 2\" width=\"600\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/qjwwpdhnw\/2017_11_09\/chamsoc2_SGQM.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<div><strong>5. Kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u1eafc-quy<\/strong>\u00a0M\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u1eafc-quy. Do \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ki\u1ec3m tra \u1eafc-quy. C\u1ea9n th\u1eadn h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng n\u00ean ki\u1ec3m tra th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u00e1y ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u00e0 d\u00e2y d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t.\u00a0<strong>6. Kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean thay d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e1t \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3<\/strong>\u00a0Vi\u1ec7c nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng xung quanh xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5p t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u00f4 t\u00f4. \u1ea2nh h\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y l\u00e0 \u1eafc quy kh\u00f3 k\u00edch, ho\u1eb7c nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng bay h\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00e8m theo vi\u1ec7c d\u1ea7u b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7c, b\u00f4i tr\u01a1n k\u00e9m h\u01a1n l\u00e0m t\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 diesel kh\u00f3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/div>\n<div class=\"article-photo inlinephoto\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/qjwwpdhnw\/2017_11_09\/chamsoc4_HSQE.jpg\" data-desc=\"Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u00f4t\u00f4 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o\" data-index=\"2\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/qjwwpdhnw\/2017_11_09\/chamsoc4_HSQE.jpg\" alt=\"6 sai l\u1ea7m khi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u00f4t\u00f4 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh 3\" width=\"600\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/qjwwpdhnw\/2017_11_09\/chamsoc4_HSQE.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<div>L\u00fac n\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3 nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean thay d\u1ea7u m\u00e1y v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m m\u00e1t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p xe s\u1ebd v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/div>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c d\u1ea7u b\u00f4i tr\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7c khi th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft l\u1ea1nh, sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ea7u c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eb7n v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd ki\u1ec3m tra d\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi thay m\u1edbi nh\u1eb1m gi\u00fap xe \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m thay d\u1ea7u th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o l\u00e0 sau m\u1ed7i 8.000km \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n<div class=\"article__source cms-source\">Ngu\u1ed3n: <a href=\"http:\/\/tienphong.vn\">tienphong.vn<\/a><\/div>\n<div>\n<hr \/>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><strong>HYUNDAI H\u1ea2I PH\u00d2NG<\/strong><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Hotline kinh doanh: 0906.026.299<\/span><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">C\u01a1 s\u1edf 1: 742 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Linh, L\u00ea Ch\u00e2n, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">C\u01a1 s\u1edf 2: 9\/10B L\u00ea H\u1ed3ng Phong, H\u1ea3i An, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Youtube: <a class=\"qi72231t nu7423ey n3hqoq4p r86q59rh b3qcqh3k fq87ekyn bdao358l fsf7x5fv rse6dlih s5oniofx m8h3af8h l7ghb35v kjdc1dyq kmwttqpk srn514ro oxkhqvkx rl78xhln nch0832m cr00lzj9 rn8ck1ys s3jn8y49 icdlwmnq cxfqmxzd ezidihy3\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCBBFDZUOt6MMCn158SEzi1w?fbclid=IwAR2PFRhuaArDd9Rp4SpaOoNTHkVwDpnqgp9LGKQ6XPSrL6u2DInzDktSeXE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCBBFDZUOt6MMCn158SEzi1w<\/a><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Facebook: <a class=\"qi72231t nu7423ey n3hqoq4p r86q59rh b3qcqh3k fq87ekyn bdao358l fsf7x5fv rse6dlih s5oniofx m8h3af8h l7ghb35v kjdc1dyq kmwttqpk srn514ro oxkhqvkx rl78xhln nch0832m cr00lzj9 rn8ck1ys s3jn8y49 icdlwmnq cxfqmxzd d1w2l3lo tes86rjd\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/HyundaiHaiPhong\/?__cft__[0]=AZWg_MrN3mXuw_x73xHW94PZY7ynzIX37e2uX8IrePs-InVby_pIV0jGkcKZbX8IH8orw6_75uJ9nxL_SThNTq0Y5vuHDILjdAcAYdWQaCUWVRrIGWXqz76EPoNl2E9NEOI&amp;__tn__=kK-R\"><span class=\"rse6dlih\">https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/HyundaiHaiPhong<\/span><\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, \u00f4t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1edfi th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t, nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5p l\u00e0m xe hay g\u1eb7p s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 h\u01a1n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 6 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i khi &#8220;ch\u0103m&#8221; xe trong th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft gi\u00e1 l\u1ea1nh. 1. Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u00e1y li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u1ea5m [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":13642,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1,30],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13760"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=13760"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13760\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":13761,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13760\/revisions\/13761"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/13642"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=13760"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=13760"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=13760"},{"taxonomy":"yst_prominent_words","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/yst_prominent_words?post=13760"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}